Major functionality
 - UV plane visualisation
 - Earth positioning

UI Enhancements
 - Click to select objects in scene
 - Scroll / shift-drag to change zoom
 - Tooltips for property inputs
 - Grid settings
 - Labelled grid axes
 - Drag to move objects
 - Input field units
 - Escape to deselect
 - Click scene to deselect

Renderer
 - Text objects
 - Camera transitions

